   ],
   "source": [
    "def outer(a, b):\n",
    "    c = function2(a, b)\n",
    "    return c\n",
    "\n",
    "def inner(a, b):\n",
    "    return a / b\n",
    "\n",
    "result = outer(1, 0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "In this example, two functions, `outer` and `inner` are defined where `outer` is simply calling `inner` with it's own parameters.\n",
